## Verification Plan

### Automated Test — Re-run scrape-audit.ts

After all changes, re-run the audit script to verify improvement:

```bash
cd /Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2
LOCAL_PAGE_BUDGET=1 npx tsx server/engines/ingestion/scrape-audit.ts
```

**Expected results:**
- Dezeen, CID Magazine, JLL MENA: should now extract items (HTML cleanup fix)
- PropertyFinder/Bayut: may remain blocked (JS-heavy, needs ParseHub projects)
- ArchDaily: should work after RSS URL change
- Firecrawl credit cache: verify it skips Firecrawl quickly without "Insufficient credits" log spam

### Direct API Test

```bash
# Test ScrapingDog with dynamic=true
npx tsx -e 'import "dotenv/config"; const r = await fetch(`https://api.scrapingdog.com/scrape?api_key=${process.env.SCRAPINGDOG_API_KEY}&url=https://www.bayut.com&render=true&dynamic=true`, {signal: AbortSignal.timeout(45000)}); console.log("Status:", r.status, "Len:", (await r.text()).length);'
```
